subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which famous fort is located in Jaipur?
question_hi: जयपुर में कौन सा मौलिक रिलेन है ?
explanation_en: Hawa Mahal is a famous palace in Jaipur known for its unique architecture.
explanation_hi: हवा महाल जापान में विशेष कालियों का एक प्लास्टिंग है, जिसमें मूर्ति से संबंध रखते हैं।
B_explanation_en: Hawa Mahal is a palace in Jaipur known for its unique architecture that is connected to the Maurya Empire.
